Comparing gradient and texture features

Gradient features are used to detect images with high contrast and texture. Current texture related features in the feature set are:

  • haralickContrast
  • haralickCorrelation
  • haralickEntropy
  • tamuraContrast
  • sobelRMS
  • gradientRMS
